item.description: IBM Sterling B2B Integrator Standard Edition 6.0.0.0 through 6.0.3.8 and 6.1.0.0 through 6.1.2.1 stores potentially sensitive information in log files that could be read by a local user. IBM X-Force ID: 247034.
